properties.value: $deviation1 = $TempA - $RefProfileMax $results1 = valueSearch($deviation1, 40h, isGreaterThan(0), 0min, true, isLessThan(0), 0min, true) $deviation2 = $TempA - $RefProfileMin $results2 = valueSearch($deviation2, 40h, isLessThan(0), 0min, true, isGreaterThan(0), 0min, true) combineWith($results1, $results2)

properties.name: Formula
properties.value:
$c1=$FV09.validValues().valueSearch(1day, isLessThan(80), 2min, isGreaterThan(80), 2min).setProperty('Stage', 'Wash')
$c2= $FV10.validValues().valueSearch(1day, isLessThan(80), 2min, isGreaterThan(80), 2min).setProperty('Stage', 'Elution')
$c3=$FV11.validValues().valueSearch(1day, isLessThan(80), 2min, isGreaterThan(80), 2min).setProperty('Stage', 'Strip')
$c4=$FV12.validValues().valueSearch(1day, isLessThan(80), 2min, isGreaterThan(80), 2min).setProperty('Stage', '2nd Pass')
$c5= $FV13.validValues().valueSearch(1day, isLessThan(80), 2min, isGreaterThan(80), 2min).setProperty('Stage', 'Loopback')
$c6=$FV14.validValues().valueSearch(1day, isLessThan(80), 2min, isGreaterThan(80), 2min).setProperty('Stage', 'Drain')
$c1.combineWith($c2).combineWith($c3).combineWith($c4).combineWith($c5).combineWith($c6)
